<task id="task_CDCFA159D1DF4DC991A006300C7B2580">
  <title>Deleting a Reusable Segment</title>
  <shortdesc>Deleting a reusable segment deletes the segment from the targeting
	 system. 
  </shortdesc>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <othermeta name="solution" content="Target" />
      <othermeta name="topic" content="Advanced" />
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <taskbody>
    <context id="context_9701455D17A34A47902A784B28EFDB4B">
      <p>When a segment is deleted, it is removed from the Segments list and
		  from any campaign that targets that segment. Be careful when deleting a segment
		  so you don't accidentally remove important targeting criteria from an active
		  campaign. 
		</p>
    </context>
    <steps id="steps_D1EBCFC3D9AD4A79BA303A4BAA0C2BB5">
      <step id="step_39D1E07B42FA423F8D717BE09B13B3D9">
        <cmd>Click 
			 <uicontrol>Segments</uicontrol> &gt; 
			 <uicontrol>Segment List</uicontrol>. 
		  </cmd>
      </step>
      <step id="step_F25557F0020C4EA09D98A2DAD38C71FE">
        <cmd>Click 
			 <uicontrol>Delete</uicontrol>. 
		  </cmd>
        <stepresult>
          <?xm-replace_text Step Result?>
        </stepresult>
      </step>
    </steps>
  </taskbody>
</task>